{"tid":278742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"來生要做日本鳥？香港最有愛嘅鳥巢喺呢度...","createTime":"2017-06-10T16:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:57:46.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1614205dc29e88af668ae79ca41ff6261d65a1f","tid":278742,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"康文署星期二在大埔廣福道剪樹殺鷺，有網民舉出日本例子，指日本無論私人公司或政府部門，都會確保雀鳥安全棲息，對人類影響減至最低。所以鳥巢下會有紙箱，膠板和木板等盛載鳥糞。「換作喺香港，擒上擒落，又要定期清理，一定俾人笑戇居！」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497012960_49d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497012960_49d4.jpg&h=5d2221bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 有網民舉出日本例子，指鳥巢下會有紙箱，膠板和木板等盛載鳥糞。</div><br />\n<br />\n但其實香港都有人自發設置「屎板」盛載鳥糞，究竟邊個咁有心，仲咁得閒收拾糞便？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497013091_c4e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497013091_c4e8.jpg&h=ea95882a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170610/56807565\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170610%2F56807565&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=bd347261\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170610%2F56807565&h=a3d0569b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170610/56807565</a></div>"},{"pid":"b7a915268f853400b9c97aeb7026fcc27ad3e04f","tid":278742,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:31:50.000Z","msg":"青衣青怡花園鳥巢下的「屎板」是該屋苑管理處十多年前設置，5至9月是燕子的繁殖期，清潔人員會在5月前清理一次，待燕子離巢了，再作清理。這麼說其實一年也只是兩至三次，要爬雲梯去清理「屎板」，比斬樹或除去鳥巢更容易，但政府卻想不出這些方法。香港觀鳥會保育主任胡明川說，「其實香港不少地方都有市民DIY鳥糞盛載器 ，但比較出名是青怡花園，因為幾乎每座都有鳥巢，而且保育得宜。」簡單的設計，在冷漠的香港，已經令人覺得好有愛。<br />\n<br />\n香港的動物保護法例罰則其實不比日本弱，日本「鳥獸保護法第8條」列明，對鳥獸之捕獲、殺傷、取卵或損傷皆屬違法，違例者最高可被判入獄一年及罰款100萬円（約7萬港元）。香港亦有《野生動物保護條例》，當中「不得狩獵或故意干擾任何受保護野生動物」和「不得取去、移走、損害、銷毀或故意干擾任何受保護野生動物的巢或蛋」兩段條文，最高可被判入獄一年和罰款10萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n斬樹以外的便便處理方法其實有很多，花盆、傘子、紙皮盒、甚至杯麵兜都行。至於被網民力讚，設計精美鳥糞盛載器，其實是由日本雀鳥研究機構 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rUw0ZO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rUw0ZO&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8b992a45\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rUw0ZO</a> 研發的，他們還上傳到網上讓大家自行打印使用！有興趣可到以下連結下載 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rdNO0h \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rdNO0h%20&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5d579293\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rdNO0h </a>。 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497012982_9a5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497012982_9a5a.jpg&h=ef5de25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 斬樹以外的便便處理方法：花盆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497013016_9b69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497013016_9b69.jpg&h=0dd19ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 攻擊性武器又得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497013017_903f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497013017_903f.jpg&h=ab37b513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 紙皮盒加膠紙亦得。</div>"},{"pid":"7cc01c45c25aeacdc10b5891b7c08be3a9c457b8","tid":278742,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多青衣嘅新聞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}